![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/b3d7e28a-9092-4b06-83cc-23ef6ae0594d/002_RAW_11202023RF_47605--26a4e399fc4667a9459c59ecdac0162e.jpeg)

After months of speculation, Drew McIntyre has officially recommitted himself to the WWE, much to the delight of fans worldwide.

McIntyre's decision to re-sign with the company comes at a pivotal moment in his career, as he continues to experience a resurgence in popularity and relevance within the wrestling world.

In recent months, McIntyre's character has undergone a compelling evolution, capturing the attention of both longtime fans and newcomers alike. His storylines with the Bloodline, Seth Rollins and CM Punk as well as his keen social media presence have reignited interest in his journey, positioning him as a pivotal figure in the ongoing narrative of WWE programming.

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/6baa37ae-8423-4663-bd84-ad5a0356288e/Screenshot_20240427_182536.jpg)

In a symbolic gesture of support and recognition, Dwayne "The Rock" Johnson gifted McIntyre with a Scottish Claymore, a traditional Scottish sword, during a recent WWE event.

**_“Man of my word_**

**_As you're a man of yours - Congratulations @dmcintyrewweon signing your new @wwe deal._**

**_As we talked about after your #WrestleMania match, I know this Scottish Claymore represents everything that you, your family and your country embody._**

**_Alba gu bràth_**

**_As you know, I wanted to personally hand deliver this gift to you at your meeting with Nick Kahn, but I had warm cheat meals and chilled tequila waiting for me_**

**_Congrats again brother and cheers to hunger, passion,climbing that mountain and always entertaining our fans._**

**_\- Final Boss”_**

As McIntyre embarks on this new chapter of his WWE journey, fans can anticipate even greater feats of athleticism, compelling storytelling, and unforgettable moments in the ring. His decision to extend his contract with the company serves as a testament to his unwavering dedication to his craft and his commitment to entertaining and inspiring audiences around the globe.

Drew McIntyre's decision to re-sign with the WWE marks a significant milestone in his illustrious career and signals an exciting continuation of his storied legacy within the wrestling industry. With his talent, passion, and undeniable star power, McIntyre is poised to continue making an indelible impact on the world of sports entertainment for years to come.